Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.68,0:00:05.98,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Within the spreading darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.02,0:00:08.65,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I pledged a vow to the revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.81,0:00:13.82,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I can't let anybody interrupt it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.90,0:00:18.95,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.46,0:00:31.71,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The future that the forbidden fruit foretells...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.92,0:00:40.18,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm going to change the dream into reality
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.89,0:00:52.02,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The ending that everybody wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.02,0:00:55.32,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Within the spreading darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.40,0:00:58.07,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I pledged our vow to the revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.15,0:01:02.95,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I can't let anybody interrupt it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.12,0:01:08.41,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Someday I'll show you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.41,0:01:17.71,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}A bright and ideal world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.18,0:01:31.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was footage that was coincidentally\Ncaptured on surveillance cameras
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.23,0:01:33.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,of the FBI agents who died in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.77,0:01:38.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please show me only\Nthe scenes of Raye Penber
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.24,0:01:42.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,passing the ticket gate,\Nriding the train, and then dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.12,0:01:43.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.70,0:01:45.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.78,0:01:46.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's right below that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.83,0:01:48.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.29,0:01:56.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Raye Penber enters through\Nthe ticket gate of Shinjuku Station at 15:11.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.92,0:01:59.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At 15:13,\Nhe rides the Yamanote Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.13,0:02:04.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he was following someone,\Nit would be difficult...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.18,0:02:06.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to conclude anything from\Nthis blurry video.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.51,0:02:09.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And at 16:42...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.64,0:02:12.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.06,0:02:18.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And at 16:42, he gets off and dies at\Nthe Tokyo Station Platform.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.78,0:02:21.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.53,0:02:22.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.65,0:02:24.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L, what's strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.57,0:02:25.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you notice something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.62,0:02:30.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging by this footage,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.37,0:02:32.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,from the time that Raye Penber got\Non the train until his death,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.75,0:02:36.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he had been riding for an hour and a half.\NThe Yamanote Line only takes an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.34,0:02:38.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That envelope is especially strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:40.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Envelope?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.18,0:02:44.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's holding that envelope
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.43,0:02:46.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,as he enters the ticket gate\Nand reaches the platform.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.10,0:02:47.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.47,0:02:49.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's carrying it.\NHe's carrying it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.18,0:02:51.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But by the time he dies...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.48,0:02:53.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:56.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki, it's amazing you noticed that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:02:59.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Envelope isn't on the list of\Narticles he left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.19,0:03:02.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means it was left in the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.36,0:03:05.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And this video of Penber's\Nfinal moments...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.32,0:03:09.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks to me as if he's desperately trying
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.53,0:03:11.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to look inside the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.29,0:03:14.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, could there be a hint there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.04,0:03:17.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it be interesting\Nif Kira was there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:18.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Couldn't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.25,0:03:21.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.30,0:03:24.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason for Kira,\Nwho can control death from a distance,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:25.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to come to the scene of the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:32.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But despite that, he may\Nhave tried something bold.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.11,0:03:42.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.36,0:03:45.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been writing criminals'\Nnames in the Death Note
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.32,0:03:48.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,for four days already\Nwithout sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:54.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have to set up a\Ndeath schedule for several months ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.41,0:03:55.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite simply...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:57.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Suppose I get hospitalized.\NPeople will say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.71,0:04:00.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"As soon as Chief Yagami's son\Nwas hospitalized,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.71,0:04:03.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"criminals have\Nstopped dying, haven't they?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:05.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:10.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But are you sure any date before the end\Nof their predestined life span is all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.26,0:04:15.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigami never use it that way,\Nso I can't say for sure, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.43,0:04:18.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In theory, any time before\Ntheir natural deaths should be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:21.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't count on you, can l?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.02,0:04:22.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:24.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.65,0:04:27.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, please wait one moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.07,0:04:28.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:34.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ukita at the NPA has received\Na phone call he's concerned about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.25,0:04:38.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then have him give the telephone\Nnumber of number five
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:41.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and have the informant call that number.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:46.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda, you can turn on your cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:47.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, please turn it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:49.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.26,0:04:57.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is Suzuki, head of the Public\NInformation division.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:04:59.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Raye Penber's fiancée?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.81,0:05:04.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Naomi Misora...\NI've heard that name somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:12.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's her...from the Los Angeles\NBB murder case...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:18.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's it... She worked under me on\Nthat case and now she's in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.04,0:05:26.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been missing\Nsince the death of her fiancé.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.38,0:05:30.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone would be depressed\Nover the death of a fiancé...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.34,0:05:31.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:32.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:39.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, the Naomi Misora I knew was\Nvery strong-willed, an excellent FBI agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:42.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She would likely be thinking\Nof catching Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.65,0:05:45.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She was with Penber.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.48,0:05:48.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She might have found a clue...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:52.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case,\Ndid Kira get to her first?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.24,0:05:57.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, from now on,\Nwe'll focus our investigation
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.87,0:06:00.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,on the people Raye Penber\Nwas investigating while in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.46,0:06:02.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He was investigating two people
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:05.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,in relation to the police\Nand the people around them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:07.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are they? Who are those two?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:12.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Deputy Director General Kitamura\Nand his family, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.59,0:06:14.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Superintendent Yagami\Nand his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.35,0:06:16.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:22.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I also wish to place wiretaps and\Nsurveillance cameras in both households.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.35,0:06:27.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to make sure this computer\Nis clean enough if anyone examines it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.53,0:06:33.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just have to hide a\Nclipping of the Death Note in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.57,0:06:38.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are skillful\Nwith your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.45,0:06:40.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're popular with the girls, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.12,0:06:44.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That has nothing to do with skill.\NIt's more about looks than skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:47.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuk, you aren't popular are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.25,0:06:51.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Surveillance cameras? Ryuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:53.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's way out of the question!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.13,0:06:55.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It would become a civil rights issue\Nif this is discovered...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.84,0:06:57.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and we'll all be fired!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.05,0:06:59.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you willing to risk\Nmore than your jobs?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.93,0:07:01.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we were\Nputting our lives on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:04.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.60,0:07:06.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the possibility that\NKira is among them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.48,0:07:12.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten percent...\NNo, five percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:15.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! All that for only a five-percent\Npossibility is a bit much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:15.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- No.\N- Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:17.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of the people\Nwe investigated so far...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.62,0:07:20.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there wasn't anyone who even\Nseemed the least bit suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.74,0:07:22.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we should look into it
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.12,0:07:24.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,even if there's only\Na one-percent chance of finding Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:26.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.79,0:07:30.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought that my family\Nwas under suspicion...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.00,0:07:32.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.\NPlease place them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.01,0:07:37.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In return, install them in every part\Nof the house! Even the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.93,0:07:39.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss a single corner!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.97,0:07:41.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.43,0:07:42.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I was planning to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.89,0:07:44.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief!\NWhat are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.14,0:07:46.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.14,0:07:48.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a wife and daughter, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.31,0:07:50.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.19,0:07:53.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in doing this\Nunless we're thorough!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:55.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:00.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.74,0:08:02.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.99,0:08:03.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.12,0:08:11.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, out of courtesy, only Yagami and l\Nwill conduct surveillance on his home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.50,0:08:16.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Watari, how long will it take to set up\Nthe wiretaps and camera monitors?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.09,0:08:18.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.84,0:08:22.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can set them up at any time once\Nwe know when both families will be out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:27.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.89,0:08:29.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.02,0:08:34.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What? No one's home yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:44.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.39,0:09:04.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Light, no one seems to be home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:06.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna play a game together?\NIt's been awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.35,0:09:10.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Light, let's play a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:12.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:17.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:26.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Couldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:28.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew he went to\Nthose lengths!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.33,0:09:32.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Could he have something in his\Nroom he doesn't want anyone to see?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.75,0:09:34.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep in mind that\Nhe's only seventeen,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.79,0:09:36.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there's nothing suspicious\Nabout his behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.51,0:09:39.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I also did that for no apparent reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:42.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever talked to him\Nabout the investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.76,0:09:43.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.72,0:09:46.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd never tell him about anything top secret\Nthat hasn't been broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:47.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.10,0:09:50.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately I haven't been returning\Nhome regularly,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:52.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and when I do, I'm too tired...\Nand just go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.27,0:09:54.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.77,0:09:57.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.90,0:10:03.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Light, you've been ignoring me!\NI'm getting mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:06.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- There don't seem to be...\N- Hey, Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:08.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,any taps planted on these clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.95,0:10:10.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.66,0:10:13.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuk, there's a possibility that there are\Nwiretaps or surveillance cameras,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:17.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,no, likely both,\Nplaced within the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.84,0:10:21.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But that piece of paper\Nwas still in your door, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:24.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That piece of paper was\Na fake to make people think
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.09,0:10:26.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it was there to see whether anyone\Nhad entered the room while I was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.97,0:10:28.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The real detector is,\Nfirst of all, my door handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.64,0:10:29.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Door handle?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.97,0:10:31.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When that door is closed,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.89,0:10:33.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the door knob naturally rises\Nto a horizontal position.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.10,0:10:35.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't rise any higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.02,0:10:38.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But whenever I close the door,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.44,0:10:42.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I purposefully lower the door knob to\Nfive millimeters below its highest position.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:46.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, when I open the door,\Nif the knob is all the way up,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.87,0:10:49.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,chances are that someone\Nwas in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.99,0:10:52.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't rely on just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.37,0:10:55.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I also put a mechanical\Npencil lead in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:10:57.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A pencil lead?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:10:59.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,On the hinge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.50,0:11:00.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After I close the door,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.67,0:11:03.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I place a mechanical pencil lead\Non the hinge at an angle
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.84,0:11:05.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so that it will break\Nif the door is opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:08.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The lead is sure to break\Nif the door is opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.68,0:11:11.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always taken it out myself\Nwhen I entered,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.43,0:11:12.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but today, it was broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.14,0:11:15.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that. I remember you doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.81,0:11:17.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The door handle and the pencil lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:19.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no doubt that someone went in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.07,0:11:21.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it probably your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:24.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My parents and sister probably\Nwouldn't notice the piece of paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:27.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's suspicious that someone\Ntook the time to put it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:29.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.74,0:11:35.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you planning to buy a book\Nto research wiretaps and surveillance?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:40.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuk, by the way,\Nwhat'll happen to your apples?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:41.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Apples?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:45.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! From the surveillance camera...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.26,0:11:48.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,if I put the apple in my mouth\Nno one can see it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.85,0:11:51.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but it'll look like it's floating\Nif I'm just holding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.26,0:11:52.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.68,0:11:54.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigami cannot die,\Nso they won't starve either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:57.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, there's no problem\Nif I don't give you any apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:12:00.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, wait just a minute, Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.73,0:12:02.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Apples are to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.36,0:12:06.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...what cigarettes and liquor\Nare to humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:09.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have withdrawal symptoms\Nif I don't have any for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:11.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of symptoms?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.99,0:12:15.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My body twists around wildly,\Nand I'll do handstands.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.62,0:12:16.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to see that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:17.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.37,0:12:19.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuk, listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.83,0:12:24.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've given L the hint that\NShinigami love apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.96,0:12:26.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:28.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you really want to eat apples...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.22,0:12:33.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,find out where all the cameras are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.14,0:12:37.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There might be a place where\Nyou can eat apples without being seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.23,0:12:40.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Ryuk, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.48,0:12:43.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!\NFinding cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.61,0:12:46.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is also interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:10.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right, I have to find cameras...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.76,0:13:14.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe my well-behaved son\Nis looking at a magazine like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.47,0:13:17.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's normal for a 17-year-old.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.93,0:13:21.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But to me, it seems like\Nhe's making an excuse, as if to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.77,0:13:23.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"l was checking to see\Nif someone was in this room...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.02,0:13:26.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"because I have magazines like these."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.44,0:13:31.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki, are you telling me that\Nyou suspect my son?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.86,0:13:32.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I suspect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.49,0:13:35.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I placed wiretaps\Nand cameras in your house
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.45,0:13:37.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,as well as\Nthe Deputy Director General's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:42.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I found a camera in the air conditioner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.59,0:13:45.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So there were cameras...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.30,0:13:48.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That probably means\Nthere are also wire taps.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.42,0:13:50.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if this is for the Kira case,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.26,0:13:53.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe the Japanese police\Nwould go this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.26,0:13:55.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is L's doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:58.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case,\Nhow far has he narrowed it down to?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.85,0:14:00.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be down to at least someone
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.69,0:14:05.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that Raye Penber was investigating\Nor he would have never gone this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.36,0:14:08.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was tricked by the cover again...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.74,0:14:11.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, in this case, I should move as if...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.49,0:14:15.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the only one being suspected\Nand being watched.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:17.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.74,0:14:20.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been preparing for\Nsomething like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:21.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I got\Nthese magazines.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.54,0:14:26.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:32.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for dinner...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:34.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:36.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.39,0:14:44.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hideki Ryuga, you're so dreamy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.69,0:14:47.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nobody in my class like him!\NNo one at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.07,0:14:49.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.15,0:14:50.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat your dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:51.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:55.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Aizawa, are the Kitamuras\Nwatching television now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.28,0:14:56.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:14:58.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aside from the Deputy Director General,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.49,0:15:00.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the four of them are watching\Ntelevision as they eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:01.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's channel four.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:06.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Watari, order the various television\Ncompanies to broadcast our banner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.13,0:15:08.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.42,0:15:08.88,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,50)\fad(250,250)}NKK Newsflash
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.92,0:15:09.38,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,50)\fad(250,250)}NKK Newsflash
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.63,0:15:11.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.38,0:15:14.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"In response to the Kira murders,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.76,0:15:20.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"the ICPO has decided to dispatch\N1,500 investigators
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.14,0:15:24.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"from various developed\Ncountries to Japan."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.23,0:15:26.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,1,500 investigators?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:28.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:31.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There should also be cameras\Nin the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.98,0:15:34.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether this news is real or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.90,0:15:37.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it's being shown to me\Nto get some kind of reaction...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:41.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L... It's the same trick you\Nused the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.45,0:15:44.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The ICPO sure is stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.46,0:15:44.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:48.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in making\Nthis announcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.17,0:15:49.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If they're going to send them in,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:51.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,they should let them come in\Nand investigate in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:55.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even those FBI agents investigating\Nin secret were killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.22,0:15:57.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The outcome will be the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.55,0:16:03.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just an overblown attempt\Nto shock Kira into exposing himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.27,0:16:06.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, it just might be completely\Nobvious to Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:11.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your son is very smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.36,0:16:14.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yeah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.49,0:16:15.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.40,0:16:19.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Are you eating potato chips\Nafter dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.57,0:16:21.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You look good right now...\Ndo you wanna get fat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.20,0:16:24.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a late night snack for\Nmy exam studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:29.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.83,0:16:32.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I found all of the cameras...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.63,0:16:35.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess even Shinigami get tired\Nwhen they try hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.67,0:16:37.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.93,0:16:40.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit complex, so pay attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:43.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to explain it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.93,0:16:45.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, time to study hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.06,0:16:49.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.81,0:16:53.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever put them here must've\Nexpected you to find some.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.86,0:16:55.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's 64 in all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.90,0:16:57.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's definitely L.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.07,0:17:00.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He had no qualms putting\Na death row inmate in his chair
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.62,0:17:01.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,when he declared war with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.62,0:17:04.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't know any limits...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:08.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So where am I going to eat\Napples in this situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.83,0:17:11.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously that's impossible, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:14.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah you can't talk to\Nme in this house, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:16.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, tell me when\Nwe go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.42,0:17:19.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I got this one right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.76,0:17:23.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging from the number of cameras,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:25.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he's planning on making\Nhis decision in a short amount of time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.22,0:17:29.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A normal person would\Nprobably give himself away, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.06,0:17:31.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you're messing with\Nthe wrong person, L...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:32.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,this is as far as you'll get.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.58,0:17:50.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've written down criminals\Nin the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.33,0:17:52.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So they will continue to die\Nover the next three weeks, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.25,0:17:57.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira has already shown L that\Nhe can control the time of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.55,0:17:58.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So in this case...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:01.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Current criminals being\Nbroadcast on the news...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.68,0:18:05.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,have to die while I'm not\Nreceiving any knowledge of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.72,0:18:06.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:08.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My withdrawal symptoms!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.23,0:18:10.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just watch, L!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:19.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With Ryuk's information\Nand my prior preparations,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.24,0:18:22.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can kill criminals\Ncurrently being broadcast
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.28,0:18:28.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,while masquerading...\Nas a regular high school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.33,0:18:33.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll solve equations with my right hand...\Nand write names with my left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:34.83,Death Note Signs/Titles Sm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz54.956\pos(469,284)}Tayoshi Murao
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.83,0:18:36.34,Death Note Signs/Titles Sm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(291,401)}Suspect: Tayoshi Murao
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.96,0:18:40.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take a potato chip...\NAnd eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.68,0:18:53.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After dinner, your son has\Ncontinued studying
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.94,0:18:56.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,without turning on\Na television or computer, hasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.98,0:18:59.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because the Entrance Exams\Nare less than ten days away...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.45,0:19:11.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now a criminal which I should\Nhave no knowledge about...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:13.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,will die of a heart attack\Nin forty seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.33,0:19:18.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The witness to my alibi is L himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.63,0:19:26.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, just a little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.48,0:19:33.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.85,0:19:34.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Watari, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:39.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Two people just broadcast on\Ntoday's nine o'clock news,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.15,0:19:42.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,a bank clerk on suspicion of\Nembezzlement during questioning...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.82,0:19:45.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And a purse snatcher\Nin a detention center...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.66,0:19:48.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,just died of heart attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.66,0:19:49.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.03,0:19:51.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,During that time in your home...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.04,0:19:54.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,your wife and daughter were\Nwatching a drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.33,0:19:56.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as that was finished,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.58,0:19:59.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,they turned off the television\Nand didn't watch anything afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.09,0:20:02.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,From just past 7:30 until now,\N11 o'clock,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.71,0:20:04.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the only thing your son has\Ndone is study.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.01,0:20:08.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira needs a face and a name to kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.72,0:20:12.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who did not watch\Nthe news, can't be Kira, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.35,0:20:15.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My family is cleared now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.69,0:20:21.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira killed people with minor crimes\Nas soon as they were broadcast, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:26.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it is the first day\Nthe cameras were installed,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.32,0:20:28.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the Yagami household is\Ninterestingly in the clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.70,0:20:35.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.71,0:20:38.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:41.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is trash day,\Nso bring out any garbage if you have any.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:44.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.51,0:20:45.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.42,0:20:49.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I always say you should be doing\Nthis without me reminding you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.93,0:20:51.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.64,0:20:57.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The weather today is nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.10,0:21:01.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I don't know if you'll do\Njust about anything if it's for yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.77,0:21:03.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,or if you're just a big spender, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.82,0:21:07.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,didn't that mini-LCD TV\Ncost 39,800 yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.78,0:21:12.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.79,0:21:28.72,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I dreamed a dream that no one could see,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.80,0:21:34.10,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I threw away everything that I didn't need
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.39,0:21:43.11,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm holding these feelings\Nthat I can't give up in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.27,0:21:49.53,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}Even if my feet fall victim\Nto the shackles of sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.61,0:21:54.08,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}In between reality and my ideal
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.91,0:21:59.79,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I can't hold back the flooding impulses
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.87,0:22:07.25,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}Because I have a strong desire\Nto accomplish
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.84,0:22:12.43,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}[deceit] [fear] [vanity] [melancholy]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.55,0:22:23.19,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm not weak enough to believe\Nany of these negative perceptions
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.65,0:22:28.98,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm a trickster who doesn't know solitude
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.37,0:22:44.46,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz0.837\pos(334,318)\fad(0,1209)}2007 To-Oh University Entrance Ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.17,0:22:44.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.21,0:22:45.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.09,0:22:48.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This proves that they don't have\Nanything on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.17,0:22:52.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a contest between L and me,\Na match of wits.
